definitions.definition: ( somewhat dated ) A general exclamation of surprise or frustration .
examples: Gee , you didn't have to kick me!

main_definition: ( somewhat dated ) A general exclamation of surprise or frustration .

definitions.definition: A command to a horse , pack animal , etc., which may variously mean “move forward ”, “go faster ”, or “ turn to the right ”.
